  03 Apr 2005; Simon Stelling <blubb@gentoo.org> grubconf-0.5.1.ebuild:
  added ~amd64

  09 Sep 2004; <rmoss@gentoo.org> grubconf-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Updating to allow usage of grub-static as well as grub as a dependency.

  22 Aug 2004; <rmoss@gentoo.org> grubconf-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Fixing the splashimage issue - force enabling it as support is present in all
  versions of grub in portage and we don't want to be mounting /boot.

  18 May 2004; Yi Qiang <khai@gentoo.org> +files/Makefile.in.in.patch,
  grubconf-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Fixed Makefile.in.in, credits go to Ghislain Bourgeois (bug #51240).

*grubconf-0.5.1 (13 Apr 2004)

  13 Apr 2004; <khai@gentoo.org> grubconf-0.5.1.ebuild:
  Version bump, fixes gcc33 compile issues.  Closes bug #40091.

*grubconf-0.5 (05 May 2003)

  05 May 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> grubconf-0.5.ebuild:
  version bump

*grubconf-0.4 (18 Apr 2003)

  18 Apr 2003; Alastair Tse <liquidx@gentoo.org> Manifest,
  grubconf-0.4.ebuild:
